               <msContents>
                  <summary>Prayer against the Tongue of People, ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ልሳነ፡ ሰብእ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="2r" to="19v" facs="002">Fols 2r–19v</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3034RepCh314">Hymn to Jesus
                                                  Christ</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                       በስመ፡ አብ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>ጸሎት [በእንተ፡] ልሳነ፡ ሰብእ፡ ዘመድ፡ ወባዕድ፡ ምቀኛ፡ ወተንኮለኛ። ናሁ፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ በኆኅያተ፡ ስምከ፡ [ካፍ።] ወበቀዳማይ፡ የውጣ፡ ዘጥንተ፡ ፊደሉ፡ አሌፍ።<gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
